B.auH=new A.cw("What is the Tournament Calendar?","The Calendar tab shows upcoming live poker tournaments sourced from PokerNews \u2014 major series like WSOP, WPT, EPT, and regional events worldwide. Each listing shows dates, buy-in, guarantee, venue, and country.")
